      "blocks": {
        "r-1": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Took my Subaru in for a check-engine light thinking I was looking at a big bill. They diagnosed it, showed me the scan, and it turned out to be a $40 sensor. Most shops would have told me I needed a new catalytic converter. These guys are honest.",
            "name": "Aaron W.",
            "title": "Hawthorne · 2019 Subaru Outback",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "r-2": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Dealer quoted me $2,400 for brake work on our minivan. Torque quoted $1,150 for the same pads, rotors, and labor — with a 2-year warranty. Done in four hours and they gave us a loaner. Won't go back to the dealer.",
            "name": "Priya M.",
            "title": "Eastmoreland · 2021 Honda Odyssey",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "r-3": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "I am genuinely terrible at car stuff. What I appreciated was that Marcus sat with me at a monitor and walked through the digital inspection report photo by photo. Didn't push anything extra. Fixed what needed fixing.",
            "name": "Dana L.",
            "title": "Sellwood · 2017 Toyota RAV4",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "r-4": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Our small business runs three delivery vans. Torque handles all of them on a rotating schedule, same-day turnaround when we need it. Fleet pricing is fair and they remember every vehicle's history.",
            "name": "Javier R.",
            "title": "Richmond · 3-vehicle fleet",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "r-5": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Bought a used Forester and brought it in for a pre-purchase inspection. They found two things the seller didn't disclose and saved me from a bad buy. Best $165 I've spent in years.",
            "name": "Kenji S.",
            "title": "Woodstock · Pre-purchase inspection",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "r-6": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Fourth time in two years — oil changes, a battery, and a set of tires. Always on time, always explained, always priced right. I send family here now.",
            "name": "Heather B.",
            "title": "Laurelhurst · Repeat customer since 2023",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": [
        "r-1",
        "r-2",
        "r-3",
